---
const spotifyPlaylistUrl = "https://open.spotify.com/playlist/YOUR_PLAYLIST_ID";
---

<section id="spotify" class="spotify-section">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2 class="heading section-title">Nuestra Playlist</h2>
    <p class="spotify-description">
      Ayúdanos a hacer nuestra boda más especial con tu canción favorita
    </p>
    
    <a 
      href={spotifyPlaylistUrl} 
      target="_blank" 
      rel="noopener noreferrer" 
      class="spotify-btn"
    >
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
        <path d="M12 0C5.4 0 0 5.4 0 12s5.4 12 12 12 12-5.4 12-12S18.66 0 12 0zm5.521 17.34c-.24.359-.66.48-1.021.24-2.82-1.74-6.36-2.101-10.561-1.141-.418.122-.779-.179-.899-.539-.12-.421.18-.78.54-.9 4.56-1.021 8.52-.6 11.64 1.32.42.18.479.659.301 1.02zm1.44-3.3c-.301.42-.841.6-1.262.3-3.239-1.98-8.159-2.58-11.939-1.38-.479.12-1.02-.12-1.14-.6-.12-.48.12-1.021.6-1.141C9.6 9.9 15 10.561 18.72 12.84c.361.181.54.78.241 1.2zm.12-3.36C15.24 8.4 8.82 8.16 5.16 9.301c-.6.179-1.2-.181-1.38-.721-.18-.601.18-1.2.72-1.381 4.26-1.26 11.28-1.02 15.721 1.621.539.3.719 1.02.419 1.56-.299.421-1.02.599-1.559.3z"/>
      </svg>
      <span>Abrir Playlist en Spotify</span>
    </a>
    
    <p class="spotify-note">
      <small>Escanea el código QR en la mesa de regalos para agregar tus canciones</small>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .spotify-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-background);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .spotify-description {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .spotify-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    padding: var(--spacing-md) var(--spacing-xl);
    background-color: #1DB954;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(29, 185, 84, 0.4);
  }

  .spotify-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(29, 185, 84, 0.5);
    background-color: #1ed760;
  }

  .spotify-btn svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .spotify-note {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
</style>
